metadata.name: Subculture, Vol. 1
metadata.description:
10-Page Preview!

Everything SubCulture in one book! Join Jason, Arthur, Noel and the entire Kingdom Comix crew as they live -- and enjoy -- the geek life in this funny and poignant look at fanboy (and fangirl) culture. 

This 336-page tome collects the critically-acclaimed four-issue mini-series plus all 501 webcomics published between 2008 and 2012. Also includes dozens of strips from guest artists, pinups, and behind-the-scenes features.
